The creation and updated dates coincide with each other (2024-09-21), which could be normal depending on the registrar policies. It is important to note that while the WHOIS data can provide useful insights, determining the legitimacy or potential risk associated with a domain often requires additional investigation beyond just the WHOIS details. It would also be advisable to check the reputation of the registrar (Gandi SAS) and verify the authenticity of the email addresses listed under Administrator, Technical, and Billing contacts through their respective RDDS services.

In conclusion, according to the given WHOIS information, there isn't enough evidence to label the domain 0FFLCE.XYZ as malicious at this point. However, continuous monitoring and verification should still be conducted to ensure the domain remains safe over time.
